9. Strengths of the System
Compression: Multi-sentence meaning in one chord.

Granularity: Preserves emotional ambiguity, grief, aspiration.

Interoperability: Works across multiple LLMs with minimal adaptation.

Device-readiness: Optimized for constrained display space.

